gomodel:SYNGO_2214  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: LRFN2 was enriched in postsynaptic density fractions.\n\n15/01/2018 Pim\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Figure legend\nfig 2F. Fractions were obtained from 2-week-old rat brains.\n\n15/01/2018 Pim\n- Overexpressed SALM1 is of mouse species: \"SALM1, SALM2, and SALM4 were obtained by PCR cloning from a mouse brain cDNA library (BD Biosciences Clontech).\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
